============================================
===       Off The Break Paintball        ===
============================================

= = = Overview = = =

Personally Coded Segments are listed below. And assisted segments are listed here.

Commentary.java

- This class required a lot of addition coding support, our original commentary system was going to
involve randomly selecting some sort of kill message based on the RNG and randomly selecting the
names of current in play players to print along with them. The system was flawed and it didn't have
the intended impact we wanted.


MatchEngine.java

- Apart from getting the match to actually run without having the ai teams bug out when they had to get some assistance
working the actual commentary into the engine and getting it to print at the right times.

Input protection / validation

- This was an improvement recommended by ai, i am familiar with coding input protection in python but i was not sure
where to start with it in java. The issue with having hans play test your game is this is the first thing he checks.

